{"tid":2407673,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"福島核電站燃料池有水溢出　東電稱不影響外部","createTime":"2021-02-14T08:36:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T08:43:03.000Z","uid":362414,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5b50d3c8872acd8c63dfa02046fca3f8a407da22","tid":2407673,"uid":362414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T08:36:04.000Z","msg":"日本福島縣對開海域7.3級地震，增至超過130人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n10年前在311大地震出現核洩漏、目前已被廢棄的福島第一核電站，有廠房的乏燃料池有水溢出。東京電力公司說，沒有水流到廠房以外，對外部無影響。同樣被廢棄的第二核電站，亦有機組的乏燃料池有微量的水溢出。<br />\n<br />\n由於路軌受損，東北新幹線部分列車服務暫停。<br />\n<br />\n地震在當地昨晚11時後發生，首都東京等地有強烈震感，福島縣發生山泥傾瀉，東北地區幾十萬戶一度停電，幾千戶仍然無水供應。首相菅義偉召開內閣會議，要求官員與地方政府密切合作，又呼籲民眾要保持警惕。<br />\n<br />\n氣象廳認為，311大地震的餘震，預計未來一星期仍可能有較強餘震。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575654-20210214.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575654-20210214.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=kmAW5qHYNhnz24jV18NLuSPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=a510add7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575654-20210214.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=37f203c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575654-20210214.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"0417300fd30bb5b376e7687f9215277567f78607","tid":2407673,"uid":88513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T08:42:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4330d8ddf68d3d93bc1950780e3e4273331853","tid":2407673,"uid":213446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T08:43:03.000Z","msg":"又係福島一帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}